          "slidetitle": "Recognising Bias in Your Practice",
          "subtitle": "Spotting the signs in everyday decisions",
          "slidecontent": "• Accepting alerts without questioning\n• Skipping your own assessment\n• Feeling reassured too quickly\n• Deferring when unsure of yourself\n• Ignoring contradicting patient signs",
          "do_not_include": false
