          "number": 7,
          "slidetitle": "Reducing Automation Bias in Practice",
          "subtitle": "Practical steps to stay critically engaged",
          "slidecontent": "• Pause before accepting AI output\n• Question unexpected normal results\n• Involve colleagues in decisions\n• Trust your clinical instincts\n• Document your own reasoning",
